<plot>Brought to trial by the blind judge Moon Dog, a visionary poet is condemned for a crime he tried to prevent. If he is to escape death by hanging at the Court of Miracles, he must surrender to the demands of the celestial street dancer, La Esmeralda. Based on characters in Victor Hugo's "Hunchback of Notre Dame," this contemporary adaptation features an international cast from 11 countries.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?458956</url></doc>
